div class=\"flex_column av_two_third  flex_column_div   avia-builder-el-9  el_after_av_one_third  avia-builder-el-last  \" ><p><div  style='padding-bottom:10px; font-size:28px;' class='av-special-heading av-special-heading-h1  blockquote modern-quote  avia-builder-el-10  el_before_av_hr  avia-builder-el-first  av-inherit-size '><h1 class='av-special-heading-tag '  itemprop=\"headline\"  >Shop Repairs<\/h1><div class='special-heading-border'><div class='special-heading-inner-border' ><\/div><\/div><\/div><br \/>\n<div  style=' margin-top:10px; margin-bottom:10px;'  class='hr hr-custom hr-left hr-icon-no   avia-builder-el-11  el_after_av_heading  el_before_av_textblock '><span class='hr-inner  inner-border-av-border-thin' style=' width:90%; border-color:#d10202;' ><span class='hr-inner-style'><\/span><\/span><\/div><br \/>\n<section class=\"av_textblock_section \"  itemscope=\"itemscope\" itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/CreativeWork\" ><div class='avia_textblock  '   itemprop=\"text\" ><h2>Power Plant Services provides expert shop repairs to ensure your turbine equipment remains operational and available at all times<\/h2>\n<p>Power Plant Services has the capabilities to complete shop repairs for steam and gas turbines from a variety of OEMs. Our shop repairs are done under the strictest of best practices, OEM guidelines, and with the highest level of quality available from an aftermarket service provider. PPS can react as quickly as your needs arise, with shop inspections and repairs performed to ensure turbine equipment reliability and maximum levels of performance.<\/p>\n<h3>The capabilities of Power Plant Services include, but are not limited to:<\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Blade \/ Bucket Installation<\/li>\n<li>Rotor Welding<\/li>\n<li>Casing Repair<\/li>\n<li>Valve Overhaul \/ Repair<\/li>\n<li>Seal Replacement<\/li>\n<li>Low Speed Balance<\/li>\n<li>Diaphragm repairs<\/li>\n<li>Turning Gears<\/li>\n<li>Auxiliary Equipment<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Power Plant Services has repair facilities in Oswego and Bedford Park, IL. We are also capable of performing field machining work on-site when parts are too large to transport to our facilities. We invite you to also consider other professional engineering services offers by PPS, including Open, Clean, Inspect, and Close (OCIC) and our Outage Parts Kits. PPS also provides expert consultation services to help your turbine operations staff with the insight needed to understand how our shop repairs can make a difference in your equipment&#8217;s performance.<\/p>\n<h3>Contact PPS today at <a href=\"tel: +17083458600\">(708) 345-8600<\/a> or send us a message to explore your immediate or upcoming project needs.<\/h3>\n<\/div><\/section><\/p><\/div>\n\n<div  class='avia-button-wrap avia-button-center  avia-builder-el-13  el_after_av_section  avia-builder-el-last ' ><a href='https:\/\/ppsvcs.com\/parts-and-services-quote-request\/' class='avia-button avia-button-fullwidth  avia-font-color-theme-color av-icon-on-hover avia-icon_select-yes-right-icon avia-color-custom '  style='background-color:#0f3e96; ' ><span class='avia_iconbox_title' >REQUEST A QUOTE<\/span><span class='avia_button_icon avia_button_icon_right' aria-hidden='true' data-av_icon='\ue83c' data-av_iconfont='entypo-fontello'><\/span><div class='av-button-description av-button-description-below'><p>Power Plant Services is always ready to meet the need of our customers, 24 hours a day, 7 days a week, 365 days of the year.<\/p>\n<\/div><span class='avia_button_background avia-button avia-button-fullwidth avia-color-custom' style='background-color:#d10202;'><\/span><\/a><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":367,"menu_order":4,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"_coblocks_attr":"","_coblocks_dimensions":"","_coblocks_responsive_height":"","_coblocks_accordion_ie_support":""},"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/ppsvcs.com\/wp-json\/wp